Subject: Wrestling at the 1988 Summer Olympics  Men's Greco-Roman 82 kg 
To: Leander
Content:
The Men's Greco-Roman 82kg at the 1988 Summer Olympics as part of the wrestling program were held at the Sangmu Gymnasium, Seongnam. The wrestlers are divided into 2 groups. The winner of each group decided by a double-elimination system.
